                         n-gram-authorship-attribution

n-gram based authoriship attribution of text.

usage:

  aa.apl [option] [args]

options:

   generate author models:

     m [max_ngram_size] [max_ngrams] [corpus_dir] [models_dir]

   attribute authorship to each of the example files based on all of the models:

     a [max_ngram_size] [equation_id] [examples_dir] [models_dir]
